The paper focuses on the use of deep learning techniques for autonomous driving, which involves computer vision, robotics, machine learning, artificial intelligence, and control systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
